dcterms:description: The Google QuickDraw dataset is the largest available sketch dataset containing 50 million sketches as simplified stroke key points in temporal order, collected via an international online game where users have 20 seconds to sketch objects from 345 classes.
dcterms:title: Google QuickDraw

dcterms:description: The TU-Berlin dataset is a smaller crowd-sourced sketch dataset that includes sketches collected from users, providing a diverse range of drawing styles.
dcterms:title: TU-Berlin
